Activities:

SplashActivity: an opening screen activity.
MainActivity: an activity that includes the 4 fragments of the app.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fragments:

FragmentByCity: a fragment to search stats for a specific city.
FragmentCountryData: a fragment that shows the stats for the whole country.
FragmentCharts: a fragment that shows selected graphs.
FragmentRedCountries: a fragment that shows the list of the world countries and their GREEN/RED rate.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------